{"tid":1822973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(正能量post)唔好因為運動暫時平靜左就自亂陣腳，過埋新年會有成績","createTime":"2020-01-13T09:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T15:41:45.000Z","uid":38991,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"52232934329e116d3e03152248977ec95bf83f76","tid":1822973,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"最近運動靜左，睇落&quot;好似&quot;就黎玩完咁，連登就變左雨傘後期咁，指責同路人既post仲多過指責敵人(你做得唔夠多，你係偽黃，你食人血饅頭 )<br />\n其實我地之前做左好多野，等多陣就有成績<br />\n<br />\n國際戰線<br />\n- 英國脫歐之後會開始馬格尼茨基人權法立法<br />\n- 美國有be water act 同第一輪制裁名單<br />\n<br />\n攬炒戰線/黃色經濟圈<br />\n- 做埋新年頂唔順既鋪會執笠炒人，已經有大公司要減薪<br />\n<br />\n香港戰線<br />\n- 等左好撚耐既監警會報告，一定會再激發香港人出黎抗爭<br />\n<br />\n只要我地堅持唔放棄，形勢會再次返黎<br />\n希望連登變返6月個時咁，多d正能量，少d放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3554d5b43eea2fe8fb8488b8ac6791ce736b4315","tid":1822973,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"【中大有人同警開閉門會議！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d02230440db81761f14ae0f64b3acf91873d3dd2","tid":1822973,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"望係咁望"},{"pid":"79d84eb85b50c935d2fb70c9aa970c9cb90491ea","tid":1822973,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"自推x1"},{"pid":"db84a2a0809de2bdac39a93bf1ae9d9569d23640","tid":1822973,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"支持正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港獨立   唯一出路</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c384953e8fdb8dafd74102a5a31f198a1200a332","tid":1822973,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"係連登堆人短視"},{"pid":"d94994743c92739ed34b342b0a2a80664b3a0f43","tid":1822973,"uid":343431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974a86b78dde19baac9b6627d0b356fbfc88a39f","tid":1822973,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c384953e8fdb8dafd74102a5a31f198a1200a332","tid":1822973,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"係連登堆人短視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"充斥住連登既最多係廢人<br />\n睇下tvb post <br />\n同埋遊行緊個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班友仲上緊連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上連登。勿認真<br />\n<br />\n上facebook仲好"},{"pid":"ef798a26738952b25cbfb3559ea7310390452708","tid":1822973,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"事實上我地真係贏緊，國際上反共意識已經成形，我地香港其實依家最重要的事就係保持團結，諗下點拉攏中立同藍絲，該去的遊行keep住去，連儂牆keep住整，擴大黃色經濟圈。仲有，開始實際上探討獨立如何實踐。食水、食物、軍事、國際關係等等。<br />\n<br />\n然後耐心等待時機成熟。冇人知道時機成熟嗰日係點但係我哋一定要做好一切準備。"},{"pid":"16a06bf86ec0dda479b8b54058874446e4f8249f","tid":1822973,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"e8fbbe9aa1d0ad2b17b6d3e2361de851b0286f56","tid":1822973,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"9cb7690252b46f39581c9cc2f02644a5b70692b6","tid":1822973,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"每個時期都有唔同階段<br />\n就好似種農作物咁<br />\n<br />\n雖然現實係殘酷<br />\n兩面可以講話完全唔對等<br />\n<br />\n但今次算係成功動員全港市民既一次<br />\n比香港人更確信自己係香港人身分，熱愛呢個香港。<br />\n<br />\n即使即使最後失敗告終，都有責任必須將今次經歷傳給下去，同時亦就只能跟一一代說聲 我地已盡力了，辛苦下一代鳥！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a14e2a61b0af4a06582c4457739fe88c5338194","tid":1822973,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"正能量！"},{"pid":"e80b9f51f8f8d275e0924888aade7ce6b3e84bc6","tid":1822973,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"所以要保持正能量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">台灣就公投完啦 甘香港人呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n一人一票<span style=\"color: red;\"> 香</span><span style=\"color: green;\">港</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">地</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">投</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">票</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港地投票 ~ 一個香港人的投票應用程式</span><br />\n下載連結：iOS / Android<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=e9eb9f9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a><br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"86920d3bb07625e68822451b0a083d614f5c6419","tid":1822973,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=68f0f13a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n【Twitter要人】國際人權監察阿頭被港府無理拒絕入境，外媒大肆報導<br